presume, the Loss you have so much lamented, and 
I do assure you, Lord (^Lofty^) has not been at (^London^) 
since his Injuries to you, but at a Seat he has just 
by this House, and there he is now: that Box which
I have now given you, he accidentally dropt in my 
Garden, nor does he know I have it; and till I see 
you as firmly his, as he has promised you should be, 
I will never leave contriving.
   [$The sight of Lord (^Lofty's^) Bond, gave poor 
(^Altemira^) a satisfaction not to be express'd; the Blood 
which had so long forsaken her Cheeks, began to run 
again in its wonted Channels, and Joy diffus'd itself 
