[$ (^Formator^) consented to her Proposal;$] [^---^]
[^AMORANDA'S (AND ALTEMIRA'S) LETTER(S) TO LOFTY OMITTED.^]
[^AMORANDA AND LOFTY MEET.^]
<P 61>
[^...^] My dearest (^Amoranda^) , 
[$ (^said he^) ,$] how shall I return this favour? with what 
joy did I receive your obliging Letter, and with 
what delight am I come to die at your feet? My 
Lord, [$ (^said^) Amoranda,$] you seem'd so very earnest in 
