stabb'd me in a thousand places. Well, [$ (^said she^) ,$] I 
am glad you are not hurt, but I wish we were at 
home.
   That, Madam, [$ (^said he^) ,$] we shall be presently; we 
have not above three Miles to your own House. [$As 
